data.description:
Charming 3-Bedroom Home on 12.26 Acres with Scenic Views

Welcome to your private oasis! This spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasts 1,968 square feet of comfortable living space on a sprawling 12.26-acre lot. 

The property features cleared land perfect for all your outdoor activities and includes a recently built addition to the main house, adding to its appeal. Additionally, there is pasture land for your use, ideal for a variety of purposes.

Situated just minutes away from the Ocoee and Hiwassee rivers as well as the Cherokee National Forest, this location is a nature lover's dream. You'll have easy access to hiking, fishing, and outdoor adventures right at your doorstep.

On the property, you'll find a small 750-square-foot home that, with some repairs, could become a fantastic income property. There's also a mobile home that has been gutted and converted into a workshop, offering endless possibilities for creative endeavors.

Enjoy the warm months in your very own above-ground pool while taking in the breathtaking views of the surrounding landscape. 

For those looking to maximize the property's potential, there are two septic tanks available for additional income properties, and sewer connections are readily available with three hookups currently on the premises.

Don't miss out on this unique opportunity to own a versatile property with income potential, beautiful scenery, and convenient access to outdoor recreation. This listing has it all!

Property to be sold as is.
